Pronunciation:
Notes: The word deck is given in the 2-volume Oxford in what seems to be the NZ sense of a wooden platform outside a house. It seems totally alien to the English experience. How many English houses have decks? Patios, yes but decks, no. Is it from Oz, California, S. Africa?
